{"tid":1140633,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"Endgame引入X-men 好過 經期隊長","createTime":"2019-05-06T03:27:42.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-06T07:42:48.000Z","uid":173003,"like":53,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"1f7a7b09518fb26c51ae479b783f82bdee070890","tid":1140633,"uid":173003,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-06T03:27:42.000Z","msg":"前排Marvel收返X-men同埋Fantastic Four嗰啲版權。我以為Marvel會喺Endgame引入X-men嗰啲角色，因為有六粒寶石、又有time travel、仲要有三個鐘自由發揮，根本想點吹都得，完全係引入X-men嘅好機會<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n之前AOU淨係洛基支權杖都已經整到女巫同埋Quicksilver。今次咁多資源，又有齊石都唔整隻X-men，一個小彩蛋都冇<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n我寧願Marvel花心思，諗下點引入X-men，放啲相關彩蛋，都唔撚想見到女權隊長喺到佔screen time，博上位<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n觀眾見到X-men，一定興奮過見到辣殺經期隊長<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n真心覺得經期浪費咗Endgame啲時間<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: green;\">正評</span>：X-men<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />經期<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">負評</span>：X-men<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />經期"},{"pid":"d571d78af33aae2c3959c31c7fc868e9076ef94b","tid":1140633,"uid":173003,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"1f7a7b09518fb26c51ae479b783f82bdee070890","tid":1140633,"uid":173003,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-06T03:27:42.000Z","msg":"前排Marvel收返X-men同埋Fantastic Four嗰啲版權。我以為Marvel會喺Endgame引入X-men嗰啲角色，因為有六粒寶石、又有time travel、仲要有三個鐘自由發揮，根本想點吹都得，完全係引入X-men嘅好機會<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n之前AOU淨係洛基支權杖都已經整到女巫同埋Quicksilver。今次咁多資源，又有齊石都唔整隻X-men，一個小彩蛋都冇<img src=\"/assets/fa